  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a1c44d26bee7f894782729c6bcff2b73, type: 3}
  m_Name: First Conversation
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  SpeakerName: Yukio
  paragraphs:
  - GOODDD MORNINGGG
  - isagi please calm down, im so exhausted
  - ahhh you work too hard gramps, you should have come out with us last night! we
    went to that new whiskey bar downtown
  - you know im working on my new recipe, i was up all night working on it
  - "oh yeah! lemme get a taste! im on a high right now so please don\u2019t piss
    me off like last time, you can bring out some intense emotions with your cooking
    and im not ready to get all mopey and sad"
  - hehe that time was funny, here let me make you something
